      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine has significant oil leaks and the transmission is slipping, meaning it will likely require a full overhaul to be reliably roadworthy again. The body shows heavy rust in several areas, the paint is severely faded, and the interior has significant tears and non-functional electronics. It currently runs and moves, but I would strongly recommend towing it rather than driving it long distances.",
