    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've gotta see this beauty in person! It\u2019s seriously in flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and is just waiting for someone to take it on a new adventure. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44500.0,
