    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46-generation M3 represents a superlative example of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. Power is delivered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system that provides seamless torque across the power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power distribution. The chassis remains in concours-level state; the rear subframe has been meticulously inspected for structural fatigue and remains factory-true. Suspension geometry is tight, utilizing MacPherson struts and multi-link rear architecture to maintain optimal contact patches. With zero evidence of thermal cycling on the plastic components and an untouched underbody, this vehicle is a benchmark for mechanical preservation and longitudinal performance.",
